creator: The Coral Media
descriptionHtml:
It is now very easy to follow the developments in the world navies.

Like everything, there is an incredible change in world navies as well. Military technologies that pioneer the civilian technologies continue to progress at a dizzying pace.

The importance of information is increasing day by day. Those who have valuable information are more advantageous than ever before, compared to their competitors.

As the Naval Library Team, we have gathered all the information necessary for the people who are working in the defense industry. This information will help organizations and individuals to enhance their situational awareness about the current and future capabilities of the world navies.

It can be used as an education tool, decision support system, operation aid, and reference book as well.

The app data includes technical information and numbers of naval ships and naval aircraft, submarines, unmanned systems, missiles, weapons, sensors, and equipment of 92 countries and the ones in development as well.

WHAT WE OFFER
Naval Library is a source of Naval Information. It gives the specifications of naval vehichles and equipment like warships, aircrafts, submarines, missiles etc.

* Up-to-date data

We continuously collect and analyze terabytes of data to create the most comprehensive, up to date, and informative data to our clients.

* One Platform

We fully collected all the navy related data into one platform – giving you easy access to a complete and comparable view of the world’s largest naval information.

* Comprehensive Data

This comprehensive reference provides information on naval vehicles, naval aircraft, unmanned maritime systems, and their equipment that in development, in production and in service with naval forces worldwide.

What’s included:

• Technical details, specifications and capability descriptions

• Operational status

• Photographs and diagrams

THE SERVICES/CONTENT WITH AND WITHOUT SUBSCRIPTION

The app has ten sections which of five are only offered to Pro users. These paid contents are "Interactive Infographics, Unmanned Systems, Missiles, Weapons, and Equipment". With the subscription user will also have the ability to use the software without an internet connection. Users will access the specifications of Warships, Submarines, Naval Aircraft, Compare, and Countries for free.

NAVAL LIBRARY PRO FEATURES (REQUIRES SUBSCRIPTION)

Offline Mode:

Going sea often means spending days without an internet connection. Thanks to the Offline Mode, you can now access the Naval Library data wherever and whenever you want.

More Information:

Detailed features of the equipment, weapons, and sensors used in the world navies. It is a unique resource for professionals. You will have all details of naval missiles, guns, torpedoes, mines, depth charges, ASW Rockets, Radars, E/O Systems, EW/Laser Systems, Sonars, Communication Equipment, Unmanned Systems and more.

Infographics:

Would you like to have a deep knowledge of warships? Our interactive infographics will help you to analyze vehicles in all aspects.
PAYMENT DETAILS
Payment will be charged to your Google Play account at the confirmation of purchase. The subscription automatically renews unless it is canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage and cancel your subscriptions by going to your Google Play account settings after purchase.

PROTECTION OF PERSONAL INFORMATION
We only store your username, password, and email just for subscription checking. All this information is securely stored and not sold nor shared with third parties.

As the Naval Library Team, we have gathered all the necessary information for the people working in the defense industry. This information will help organizations and individuals to enhance their situational awareness about the current and future capabilities of the world navies.
It can be used as an education tool, decision support system, operation aid, and reference book.
The app data includes technical information and numbers of warships and naval aircraft, submarines, unmanned systems, missiles, weapons, sensors, and equipment of 92 countries and the ones in development as well.
WHAT WE OFFER
Naval Library is a source of Naval Information. It gives the specifications of naval vehicles and equipment like warships, aircraft, submarines, missiles.
* Up-to-date data
We continuously collect and analyze terabytes of data to create the most comprehensive, up-to-date, and informative data for our clients.
* One Platform
We fully collected all the navy-related data into one platform – giving you easy access to a complete and comparable view of the world's largest naval information.
* Comprehensive Data
This comprehensive reference provides information on naval vehicles, naval aircraft, unmanned maritime systems, and their equipment in development, production, and service with naval forces worldwide.
What's included:
• Technical details, specifications, and capability descriptions
• Operational status
• Photographs, videos, documents, and diagrams
THE SERVICES/CONTENT WITH AND WITHOUT SUBSCRIPTION
The app has twelve sections, of which six are only offered to Pro users. These paid contents are "Interactive Infographics, Unmanned Systems, Missiles, Weapons, Equipment and Quiz." With the subscription, the user will also have the ability to use the software without an internet connection. Users will access the specifications of Warships, Submarines, Naval Aircraft, Compare, and Countries for free.
NAVAL LIBRARY PRO FEATURES
Offline Mode: Going to the sea often means spending days without an internet connection. Thanks to the Offline Mode, you can now access the Naval Library data wherever and whenever you want.
More Information: Detailed features of the equipment, weapons, and sensors used in the world navies. It is a unique resource for professionals. You will have all details of naval missiles, guns, torpedoes, mines, depth charges, ASW Rockets, Radars, E/O Systems, EW/Laser Systems, Sonars, Communication Equipment, Unmanned Systems, and more.
Infographics: Would you like to have a deep knowledge of warships? Our interactive infographics will help you to analyze vehicles in all aspects.
Quiz: Do you want to create and take quizzes? With the help of Quiz function, you will easily recognize naval vehicles. With this app you can create and take quizzes.
Videos, Documents, and News: Now you can access every detail of the related vehicle or equipment easily. We continuously collect all open-source data including videos, documents, and news.
PAYMENT DETAILS
Payment will be charged to your Google Play account at the confirmation of purchase. The subscription automatically renews unless it is canceled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. Your account will be charged for renewal within 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage and cancel your subscriptions by going to your Google Play account settings after purchase.
PROTECTION OF PERSONAL INFORMATION
We only store your username, password, and email just for subscription checking. All this information is securely stored and not sold nor shared with third parties.
